para_trans: Regarding administrative approval of the budget for the conservation and repair work of the state protected monument of Ahmednagar.
Department of Tourism and Cultural Affairs
Government Decision No: Monuments 2024 / Q. No.66 / CC3
Martyr Rajguru Chowk, Madam Cama Marg,
Read: Letter from the Director, Directorate of Archaeology and Museums, Mumbai Go to No. Monuments 2024/613, dated 14.02.2024.

Raghobadadawada, Ta. Kopargaon, District Ahmednagar is a state protected monument in the division.
